{{Expand Italian|Associazione bancaria italiana|date=March 2016}} 
'''Associazione Bancaria Italiana''' is the [[trade association]] of Italian banks. The association was found in 1919, few years after the Association of [[Associazione di Fondazioni e di Casse di Risparmio S.p.A.|Italian saving banks]] (ACRI found 1912), the Association of Italian rural credit union (''Cassa Rurale ed Artigiana'' found 1915) and more than 40 years after [[Associazione Nazionale fra le Banche Popolari|the Association of people's banks of Italy]] (''Banca Popolare'', found 1876).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.abi.it/Pagine/ABI/Storia.aspx|title=Storia|trans-title=Story|access-date=24 April 2016|publisher=Associazione Bancaria Italiana|language=Italian}}</ref> 
==Chairmen==
* Maurizio Sella ([[Banca Sella Group|Banca Sella]])
* Giuseppe Mussari ([[Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena]], ?–2013)
* Antonio Patuelli ([[Cassa di Risparmio di Ravenna]], 2013–)

