{{Infobox person | name = Gene Yoonsoo Yoon | image = | alt = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1945|09|09}} | birth_place = [[Hwaseong, Gyeonggi]], [[South Korea]] | death_date = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} or {{Death-date and age|Month DD, YYYY|Month DD, YYYY}} (death date then birth date) --> | death_place = | nationality = | other_names = | occupation = Fila chairman | known_for = }} {{Infobox Korean name | hangul = 윤윤수 | hanja = 尹潤洙 | rr = Yun Yun-su | mr = Yun Yun-su | context = | img = | caption = }}
'''Yoon Yoon-su''', commonly known in English as '''Gene Yoon''' (Korean 윤윤수; [[Hwaseong, Gyeonggi|Hwaseong]], 9 September 1945) is a South Korean business man. He is the current chairman of [[Fila (company)|Fila]].<ref>[http://www.hankyung.com/news/app/newsview.php?aid=2012040607441 윤윤수 휠라·아큐시네트 회장 "타이틀리스트 M&A, 하버드서 강의하겠다네요"] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233035/http://www.hankyung.com/news/app/newsview.php?aid=2012040607441 |date=March 3, 2016 }}</ref>
==Biography== Yoon graduated from [[Seoul High School]] in 1964, and [[Hankuk University of Foreign Studies]] Department of [[Political Science]] & [[Diplomacy]] in 1974. He started his career with [[Korea Shipping Corporation]] (KSC) before working in merchandising from [[JC Penney]] October 1975 to July 1981.<ref>[http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/nes/biz/2013/04/w328_125921.html Getting to know Gene Yoon<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> He then worked for Hwasung Co., Ltd. till March 1984 as export director, then becoming chairman of [[Care Line Corp]]. From June 1991 until the present he has been Chairman & CEO of [[Fila (company)|Fila]] Korea Ltd., organising a buyout of Fila brand in 2007.<ref>Forbes 181 p68 2008 "43% from its peak in 1997, Fila is taken private in a $350 million purchase by Sports Brands International, a unit of private equity firm Cerberus Capital Management. 2007 New Fila Chief GENE YOON orchestrates buyout of Fila brand for $450 ..."</ref><ref>Korea Trade & Investment 19 2-6 p58 "GENE YOON parlayed that strategy into launching one of Korea's most spectacular foreign business success stories. Just ten years after opening its doors with a capitalization of $350,000, sportswear-company Fila Korea achieved an annual."</ref>
He is also currently executive vice chairman of [[Korea International Trade Association]].
